text:
 @KStarDid 
Agreed with Sabbath but album choices maybe, Volume 4,  Master of Reality and  Black Sabbath 
Throw in Stained Class, Defenders of the Faith and Painkiller plus UFOs Lights Out and you've got a great day's tunes.

@RipMudafuka69 MLG it is Finally, although the rap, hiphop and techno music has been the music for such a long time, people are feeling the message of metal music once again. Music is the only thing that could unite us, music is not and should never be the main instrument of diversing people even more...
Let me give you a tip, listen to music from the late sixties, seventies and even the eighties.... And then came metal...
You will find a treasure...
